# Google Drive source for INDmoney report files.
# Share the Drive FOLDER and the files inside it as "Anyone with the link – Viewer".
# Create an API key in Google Cloud Console, enable the "Google Drive API", and
# restrict the key to that API (and your deploy domain via HTTP referrers).
#
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in the values. Vite only exposes vars
# prefixed with VITE_ to the browser.

VITE_GDRIVE_FOLDER_ID=your_drive_folder_id_here
VITE_GDRIVE_API_KEY=your_drive_api_key_here
